Class StringSetPropertyValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vngx.jsch.config.PropertyValidator
      • org.vngx.jsch.config.StringSetPropertyValidator

  • public class StringSetPropertyValidator
extends PropertyValidator
    Implementation of PropertyValidator which validates by checking if a string property is contained in the set of allowed values passed to the constructor.
    Author:
    Michael Laudati
